description:
You'll feel like you never left your cozy bed in these pants lined with soft flannel. The nylon ripstop shell is quick-drying layer that sheds dirt, slush and snow. The lining makes them warm enough for cold winter walks, hiking or relaxed-pace snowshoeing.Made of a stretchy, quick-drying nylon and spandex blend with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish to shed water and dirt.Fully lined in warm polyester flannel with a cozy brushed finish.Zipper fly with button closure.Zippered pocket on seam and zippered back pockets keep your stuff safe when you're active.Straight leg openings.

